readme:
Service Usage

Online visa application applicant submits initial data including biographic details, entry document details and visa subclass specific details required to calculate eligibility.

Initial data is submitted to the visa processing system which returns the following

  • Eligibility
  • Cost
  • Additional Data Capture Requirements
